display_long_description:
**Your day starts with a full inbox... and ends with organizing a trip to London. Ready to get it all organized?**

This app puts you at the center of an intense workday: urgent calls, important emails, unexpected messages... everything comes to you in real time. Your mission: structure your schedule effectively, make quick decisions, and prioritize what really matters. Every choice you make will affect the pace and results of your day.

Manage conflicts, adapt your schedule to last-minute meetings, respond thoughtfully to your contacts, and don't lose sight of your main objectives. The interface combines elements of interactive narrative and productivity simulation to offer an immersive and dynamic experience.

But work doesn't end with office hours. At the end of the day, you'll have to plan your next trip to London: dates, accommodations, meeting schedule, budgets, documentation... Will you be able to balance work demands with strategic trip planning?

Main features:

- Dynamic scheduling and decision-making system.

- Emails, calls, and messages generated in real time based on your actions.

- Trip planning with multiple variables to manage.

- Ideal for productivity enthusiasts, office simulators, and strategic planners.

Organize your day. Plan your future. It all starts with a notification.
